&lt;h4 id=&#34;wustctf-2020level2&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#wustctf-2020level2&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; [WUSTCTF 2020]level2&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
