&lt;h5 id=&#34;bjdctf-2020babyrop2&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#bjdctf-2020babyrop2&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; [BJDCTF 2020]babyrop2&lt;/h5&gt;
